00:29:07.540 --> 00:29:09.370
that a single caring
individual could

00:29:09.370 --> 00:29:11.770
make a difference
in this huge world,

00:29:11.770 --> 00:29:15.190
and might even help determine
the course of events."

00:29:15.190 --> 00:29:18.310
