00:30:50.700 --> 00:30:51.999
And we might.

00:30:51.999 --> 00:30:53.040
In fact, more than might.

00:30:53.040 --> 00:30:55.830
I think we have a good
chance of actually making it

00:30:55.830 --> 00:30:57.420
as a civilization.

